<plot>On the cursed island continent of Lodoss, a party of adventurers becomes caught up in the struggle against a plot to conquer Lodoss and revive a long-dormant ancient evil deity. This thirteen-part Japanese television series is based on a series of Japanese novels, and is notable among other things for its inclusion of elements from the Dungeons &amp; Dragons (TM) role-playing game.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?340310</url></doc>
